summary: An Ordinance granting License for the sale of Intoxicating Liquors by Wholesale and Retail, to the alley between Twenty-fourth and Twenty-fifth Avenue from E. Pine to E. Howell Street in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 15623, creating Local Improvement District No. 1454 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
